name: wdl-aid
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "WDL-AID" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 96d1706cdca8d83d9df096aa4a4dfa3ad44581f1cc530f214dcc5bac115dddc7

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  entry_points:
    - wdl-aid=wdl_aid.wdl_aid:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - jinja2
    - miniwdl >=1.0
    - python >=3.6

test:
  imports:
    - wdl_aid
    - wdl_aid.templates
  commands:
    - wdl-aid --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/biowdl/wdl-aid
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Automatic Input Documentation for WDL workflows
  doc_url: https://wdl-aid.readthedocs.io/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - DavyCats
    - rhpvorderman
